{"tid":602313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 街頭整蠱途人玩出禍 踢傷女子要賠$58萬","createTime":"2018-03-23T02:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T03:55:12.000Z","uid":122101,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"12377a4ea82a20b758fc6834f8fddd30965702d7","tid":602313,"uid":122101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"西班牙一名男子貪得意拍下自己在街頭偷襲途人的整蠱片段，要賠償6萬歐元（58萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n片段中，24歲的蒙特亞萊格雷（Mario Garcia Montealegre）在巴塞隆拿從後踢向一名48歲女子的小腿，女子應聲倒地，屁股着地，慘叫一聲，回頭向着拍攝者說了一句粗口。<br />\n該名女子足踝扭傷，左膝和左腕受輕傷、頸痛，需要請病假75天。<br />\n加泰羅尼亞警方引應這片段，通緝蒙特亞萊格雷，而片段在網上瘋傳後，他已向警方自首。控方最初要求蒙特亞萊格雷賠償4.5萬歐元（約44萬港元），但蒙特亞萊格雷為了表示改過決心，同意向受害女子賠償6萬歐元。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\nLINK:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57979042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979042&d=dXbaxH59gujBFwsrddcCrp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=adccdb0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979042&h=0989bfdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57979042</a><br />\n<br />\n小學雞式整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b64be290b7dab82dfec80e6ef375bbc2dccb31","tid":602313,"uid":142532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"On9仔"},{"pid":"80c2323e82cd49fc24f805a86b2fe0eb8f17aa5d","tid":602313,"uid":31990,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"賠唔起先有野睇,條友有錢到自願加碼,屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0b41fd1dc7c737cc16a510e2f64d7273878115","tid":602313,"uid":16061,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"80c2323e82cd49fc24f805a86b2fe0eb8f17aa5d","tid":602313,"uid":31990,"like":21,"dislike":0,"s